data.description: Don't miss this like-new 3-bedroom, 2-bath Kerry Floor plan, moved into in 2023, located in Meridian Forest @ Avalon, a highly desirable community with fantastic amenities, including a community pool, kayak lake, dog park, pickleball court, bocce ball, horseshoes, and picnic area. Conveniently located only a short drive to Oak Island, Southport, Myrtle Beach, and Wilmington.This home features 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths, a spacious kitchen with a granite island and counters, stainless steel appliances, 9 ft ceilings, and an 8x10 covered patio. The home is prewired and bracketed for ceiling fans in the bedrooms, living room, and porch to make installation easy. Refrigerator, washer & dryer, and window blinds throughout are included.This property is truly a gem, ready for you to call home.
